---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Home">
  <div class="border-t-4 border-t-sky min-w-full">
  <div class="stack h-96 w-full  bg-white ">
    <img class="object-cover object-right-top h-96 w-full " src="/assets/images/hero/20210626.adefua-day-of-action.dancers.02.jpg"/>
    <div class="bg-gray-900 h-96 w-full bg-opacity-50"></div>
    <div class="h-full flex justify-around items-top">
      <img class="rounded-full h-96 mx-20 relative top-16 hidden lg:block z-10 shadow-lg" src="/assets/images/rvcd-logo.png" />
      <h1 class="font-heading text-white text-3xl sm:text-4xl xl:text-5xl font-base w-4/5 lg:w-full ml-auto mr-auto lg:mr-20 lg:ml-0 mt-20 lg:mt-5 xl:mt-10 leading-relaxed sm:leading-relaxed xl:leading-relaxed tracking-widest opacity-90 text-center lg:text-right">
        Unifying Communities of Rainier Valley through 
        Arts and Culture
      </h1>
    </div>
    <button class="place-self-end self-end mb-5 mr-5 opacity-50 hover:opacity-80">
			<svg class="fill-current text-white" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="30px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="30px"><path d="M0 0h24v24H0V0z" fill="none"/><path d="M11 7h2v2h-2zm0 4h2v6h-2zm1-9C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm0 18c-4.41 0-8-3.59-8-8s3.59-8 8-8 8 3.59 8 8-3.59 8-8 8z"/></svg>
		</button>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-sky mt-0 stack w-full">
    <div class="wave-clip bg-gray-800 w-full opacity-20 h-1/4 sm:h-1/3 lg:h-full"></div>
    <div class="mx-auto pt-10 lg:pt-24 pb-10 px-6 max-w-6xl w-full grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6 z-10">
      <div class="w-full  text-white">
        <h2 class="font-secondary text-3xl text-center">Your creative district will</h2>
        <div class="gradient-line mt-3 mb-4"></div>
        <ul class="text-2xl mx-6">
          <li class="flex items-top mb-2"><svg class="inline-block mr-3 h-7 w-3 flex-none fill-current" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="24px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24px" fill="#000000"><path d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M12 2C6.47 2 2 6.47 2 12s4.47 10 10 10 10-4.47 10-10S17.53 2 12 2z"/></svg>Unify the creative community and build deeper connections.</li>
          <li class="flex items-top mb-2"><svg class="inline-block mr-3 h-7 w-3 flex-none fill-current" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="24px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24px" fill="#000000"><path d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M12 2C6.47 2 2 6.47 2 12s4.47 10 10 10 10-4.47 10-10S17.53 2 12 2z"/></svg>Foster new opportunities for collaboration.</li>
          <li class="flex items-top mb-2"><svg class="inline-block mr-3 h-7 w-3 flex-none fill-current" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="24px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24px" fill="#000000"><path d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M12 2C6.47 2 2 6.47 2 12s4.47 10 10 10 10-4.47 10-10S17.53 2 12 2z"/></svg>Support, facilitate and grow arts & cultural events.</li>
          <li class="flex items-top mb-2"><svg class="inline-block mr-3 h-7 w-3 flex-none fill-current" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="24px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24px" fill="#000000"><path d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M12 2C6.47 2 2 6.47 2 12s4.47 10 10 10 10-4.47 10-10S17.53 2 12 2z"/></svg>Advocate for arts-centered development.</li>
          <li class="flex items-top mb-2"><svg class="inline-block mr-3 h-7 w-3 flex-none fill-current" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="24px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24px" fill="#000000"><path d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M12 2C6.47 2 2 6.47 2 12s4.47 10 10 10 10-4.47 10-10S17.53 2 12 2z"/></svg>Establish a thriving creative hub.</li>
          <li class="flex items-top mb-2"><svg class="inline-block mr-3 h-7 w-3 flex-none fill-current" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="24px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24px" fill="#000000"><path d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M12 2C6.47 2 2 6.47 2 12s4.47 10 10 10 10-4.47 10-10S17.53 2 12 2z"/></svg>Provide for economic stabilization.</li>
          <li class="flex items-top mb-2"><svg class="inline-block mr-3 h-7 w-3 flex-none fill-current" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="24px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24px" fill="#000000"><path d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M12 2C6.47 2 2 6.47 2 12s4.47 10 10 10 10-4.47 10-10S17.53 2 12 2z"/></svg>Preserve cultural diversity and artistic character.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="">
        <div class="gradient-line mb-10 block lg:hidden "></div>
        <img class="h-auto mx-auto max-w-sm rounded-xl  border-4 border-white" src="/assets/images/rvcd-map.png"/>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
